doc_summary_long: Stephen Hawking's PhD thesis was accessed more than two million times within days of it being made available to the public, it has been revealed. 'I'd hazard a guess that Prof Hawking's PhD thesis is also the most accessed item from any research repository ever. The next most read PhD thesis has received just 7,960 downloads in 2017.

doc_title: Professor Stephen Hawking's PhD viewed two million times
